quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,85,"Àti (Ànábì) Zakariyyā, Yahyā, ‘Īsā àti ’Ilyās; gbogbo wọn wà nínú àwọn ẹni rere."
  6,86,"Àti ’Ismọ̄‘īl, al-Yasa‘, Yūnus àti Lūt; ìkọ̀ọ̀kan wọn ni A ṣoore àjùlọ fún lórí àwọn ẹ̀dá (àsìkò wọn)."
  6,87,"Àti pé nínú àwọn bàbá wọn, àrọ́mọdọ́mọ wọn àti àwọn arákùnrin wọn, A tún ṣà wọ́n lẹ́ṣà. A sì fi wọ́n mọ̀nà tààrà (’Islām)."